    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "serotonin syndrome sounds kinda extreme lol. i've read online that if you just take a low dose of the supplement it's fine and helps with the side effects of the sertraline. like, since it's just a natural herb, it shouldn't really mess with the prescription that much, right? i just need a little extra help to get through these exams.",
