    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i really dont have time to wait for a doctor appt before my exams start next week... i'm just looking for some reassurance. i've seen people on forums say that as long as you don't take a massive amount of both at the same time, you'll be fine. isn't the risk really low if i just use it as a mild supplement? like, can't i just test it out with a small amount to see if it helps?",
